text: I Do Not Care If We Go Down in History as Barbarians () is a 2018 Romanian Czech German French Bulgarian World War II black comedy movie directed by Radu Jude and starring Ioana Iacob, Alex Bogdan, Alexandru Dabija. ==Other websites== * Category:2018 movies Category:2010s war movies Category:2010s black comedy movies Category:Romanian comedy movies Category:Czech comedy movies Category:German comedy movies Category:French comedy movies Category:Bulgarian movies Category:World War II movies Category:Movies directed by Radu Jude
